      "role": "user",
      "content": "If these studies are being used to support the idea of genetic differences, what are the actual biological or evolutionary arguments they use to explain why these specific patterns would emerge in different populations? Like, what's the logic behind linking these IQ gaps to evolutionary history? I want to understand the actual reasoning used by the proponents.",
